name: Men's T-Shirt // Mr. Solo Dodo // Connection Collection: The RCA // Video
description:
"So why the Dodo bird? Because it's XTINCT you big dummy! Okay. So why the RCA colors? Well with all the technology going around these days; Fiber optics, S-Videos & Usb's, we tend to forget that it's the RCA cable that started it all! The N64, Turntables, MPC's, these are all things that wouldn't have been possible if it wasn't for this little connector we know as the RCA. So rep your respect for the cable that made it all possible, and the Dodo who happen to be caught in the middle of all of it. Also, all orders from our Connection Collection, receive a free 6ft RCA cable with your purchase!"
XTINCT Clothing™ TINC about what you wear. /////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////// Limited to: 12 Other Colorways: White on Black (Left Audio) Red on Black (Right Audio)
